title: Flora of the Marquesas Islands
text:
The <a href="Marquesas%20Islands">Marquesas Islands</a> have a diverse <a href="flora%20%28plants%29">flora</a>, with a high rate of <a href="endemic%20%28ecology%29">endemism</a>. They are in the floristic Polynesian subkingdom of the <a href="Oceanian%20realm">Oceanian realm</a>.

Other plants.
"<a href="Pelagodoxa%20henryana">Pelagodoxa henryana</a>", the only species in the genus "<a href="Pelagodoxa">Pelagodoxa</a>", is a palm tree that is <a href="endemism">endemic</a> to the Marquesas Islands.
